      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GINGER RUSH (2) finds it hard to break through. Better run when finding the frame last time though, finishing second (16.27) at this track. Has a good record here including six wins. Capable of going well again. POP'S GIRL (3) drew an outside box and was game in defeat when only 0.9 lengths from the winner Lochinvar Hornet in third(19.33) at Hobart. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Expecting another good run. NEWS FLASH (1) was out of the placings last time when eighth at this track (16.61) but did record best time of the card when winning four back. Form here at the trip sound including eight wins. Goes well out of this box with a win and two minor placings. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. MOLLY POTION (8) was strongly fancied on the back of a win two starts ago but finished sixth last time (16.90) at this track.",
